This is the INSTALL file.
For explanation of each step see bellow.

* Quick installation:

git clone git://repohost/core
git clone git://repohost/api
cd api
ln -sf api.dev.ini etc/api.ini
./bin/make
vim etc/api.dev.ini
cd ..
git clone git://repohost/app
cd app
ln -sf app.dev.ini etc/app.ini
./bin/make
vim etc/app.dev.ini

--

* Installation steps are:

1. clone the core repo (dependency)

    $ git clone git://repohost/core

2. clone the api repo (dependency)

    $ git clone git://repohost/api

3. update the configuration file etc/api.dev.ini

    $ cd api
    $ vim etc/api.dev.ini

4. make the link to the configuration file in use

    $ cd api
    $ ln -sf api.dev.ini etc/api.ini

5. execute bin/make in the api
    
    $ cd api
    $ ./bin/make

6. clone the app repo

    $ git clone git://repohost/app

7. update the configuration file etc/app.dev.ini

    $ cd app
    $ vim etc/app.dev.ini

8. make the link to the configuration file in use

    $ cd app
    $ ln -sf app.dev.ini etc/app.ini

9. execute bin/make in the app
    
    $ cd app
    $ ./bin/make

10. you are done !!
